      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that runs and drives well and has clearly been kept up better than an average used vehicle. Overall presentation is strong inside and out, with only normal light wear for its age such as minor cosmetic blemishes and typical signs of use, but nothing that changes the fact that it shows well and feels like a solid, dependable car. Interior is in good shape, exterior is presentable, and a buyer should expect a well-rounded used car that is ready to be driven and enjoyed.",
