      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle for buyers who want dependable transportation at an accessible price. This car shows its age and is best suited for someone who values straightforward utility over cosmetics, but it still offers solid everyday potential and an affordable path into ownership. An excellent choice for a commuter, backup vehicle, or project-minded buyer looking for real value.",
