    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without the drama? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid, honest option for someone who wants dependable basic transport at a budget-friendly price. Great as a first car, a backup vehicle, or a practical runaround. If you appreciate straightforward deals and a car that still has plenty to offer, this one is well worth a look.",
