      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a tough-running powertrain and plenty of usable life left for someone who wants dependable transportation without a big payment. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related blemishes, but the engine pulls well, the transmission does its job, and it remains a practical, no-nonsense car for commuting, errands, or a backup vehicle. A great candidate for someone who appreciates function over flash and wants an affordable car with honest character.",
