      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real personality\u2014the kind of honest, well-traveled machine that still turns heads for all the right reasons. It has that classic everyday-driver spirit: simple, usable, and full of potential for someone who wants affordable wheels with character instead of something forgettable. Whether you need a practical runabout, a first project, or a budget-friendly set of keys to get moving, this one offers a chance to make it your own without a huge upfront cost.",
