      "description": "Honest, budget-friendly transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle shows its age, but it starts, runs, and offers an affordable path into ownership for the right buyer. A practical choice for someone who values low upfront cost, a dependable basic driver, or a project with room to make it your own. Priced to reflect condition while still delivering solid value.",
